{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dive into Ink.</strong>, an explosive and colorful roguelike RPG adventure where every game is a new journey waiting to be discovered. Play <strong>solo</strong> or team up with friends in local <strong>co-op mode</strong> with up to three players and face the challenges that await you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146270/extras/2c.gif?t=1737302461\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to the World of Ink!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Ink., you\u2019ll venture through the pages of an enchanted book, battling a myriad of unique monsters and formidable bosses. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Discover mysterious items, upgrades, and magical cards, combining them to unlock infinite synergies and unique powers every time you play. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The precious ink drops you collect are key to your survival: use them wisely to trade, acquire extraordinary items, and upgrade your equipment. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every strategic decision could change the course of your adventure!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Protagonists and Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Live the dreams of young Liam, a creative child who brings incredible stories to life through his drawings. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as his three adorable plush kittens\u2014Spok, Smuk, and Skrat\u2014and take on epic challenges. Choose from various game difficulties, unlock new items and cards. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each game with the unlocked characters will be a fresh and thrilling adventure.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146270/extras/4c.gif?t=1737302461\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Discover Your Unique Style!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each character in Ink. offers a distinct playstyle and a customizable weapon. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build and assemble your weapon in surprising ways, enhancing each component individually or replacing it with unique pieces and effects. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Customize your equipment to create lethal combinations and adapt your strategy to each challenge you encounter.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">The Book of Ink.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The magical book of Ink. will take you through nine unique chapters, each with its own atmosphere and challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start from the first page and progressively unlock new chapters, choosing your path and discovering new adventures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each chapter offers special pages where you can trade, obtain powers, discover rare items, or face special challenges. No story will ever be the same, and you will always be the protagonist!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146270/extras/1c.gif?t=1737302461\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to dive into a world of endless fantasy and strategy. The world of Ink. is in your hands: are you ready to write your legend?</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"The Well of Fortune","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146270/0ed54d27c6c255b9ab317c4371f4f24131d327ac.jpg"},{"name":"The Witch","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3146270/dd7f9d9a3eb66e6a945233dd8bf58510148ecb29.jpg"},{"name":"How Lucky!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.co